@endpoint GET /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Sql/servers/{serverName}/auditingSettings
@desc Lists auditing settings of a server.
@returns(200) Successfully retrieved server auditing settings.

@endpoint GET /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Sql/servers/{serverName}/databases/{databaseName}/auditingSettings/{blobAuditingPolicyName}
@desc Gets a database's blob auditing policy.
